      "level": {
        "value": 1
      },
      "isComplex": true,
      "disable": "<p>@Check[computers|dc:13] (trained) overrides the security program; @Check[crafting|dc:15] or @Check[thievery|dc:15] (trained) disables the hardlight projector; @Check[diplomacy|dc:17] convinces the Archivist to reconsider. Four total successes are required to end the program.</p>",
      "routine": "<p>(1 action) Archivist 404 fires one laser at each intruder in the archive as one action. It takes a cumulative â€“1 status penalty to its attack rolls for each successful check the PCs have made to disable it.</p>",
